                            <comment id="16002605" author="githubbot" created="Tue, 9 May 2017 12:27:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;GitHub user iv-m opened a pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/3002&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/3002&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-5203&quot; title=&quot;Percentilles are calculated incorrectly&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-5203&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-5203&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Metrics: fix resetting of histogram sample&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Without the histogram cleanup, the percentiles are calculated&lt;br/&gt;
    incorrectly after purging of one or more samples: event counts&lt;br/&gt;
    go out of sync with counts in histogram buckets, and bucket&lt;br/&gt;
    with lower value gets chosen for the given quantile.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    This change adds the necessary histogram cleanup.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can merge this pull request into a Git repository by running:&lt;/p&gt;

